Package: afnews
Title: Africa news data collection.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Armel",
           family = "SOUBEIGA",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "armel.soubeiga@yahoo.fr",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A package to scraping all news of all countries of Africa. The news is by country and by date range. The data returned are: title, contents, comments, journal name and category.
